Game MUST display two paddles, one on each side of the play screen.
Game MUST display a ball on the play screen.
Ball MUST move automatically once the game starts.
Player MUST be able to move their own paddle.
Game MUST move opposing paddle according to ball movement.
Game MUST display current score for both players.
Ball MUST reverse direction when hitting a paddle.
Ball MUST bounce when hitting play arena ceiling/floor.
Player MUST receive point when ball exists play arena on opposite side.
Game MUST reset ball to center of play arena when point is scored.
